<h4>What I do?</h4>
<ul>
  <li>I only make websites using <b>React + Firebase</b> or <b>PHP + MySQL</b> for full-stack websites.</li>
  <li>I make vanilla websites, but only for front-end development.</li>
  <li>I create logos specifically for websites.</li>
  <li>I provide deployment services for React websites, but without custom domain names.</li>
  <li>I offer front-end web development & design.</li>
  <li>I deliver source code to clients only after full payment is received.</li>
  <li>I deliver the production deployment only after full payment is received.</li>
</ul>

<br/><br/>

<h4>What I don't do?</h4>
<ul>
  <li>I do not deploy PHP + MySQL websites.</li>
  <li>I do not do graphic design, as I am not a graphic artist.</li>
  <li>I do not host websites; I rely on third-party web hosting services. I am a web developer, not a software engineer.</li>
  <li>I do not create 3D models, as I am not a 3D artist.</li>
  <li>I do not work with custom domain names for React websites. Clients must provide their own domain name.</li>
  <li>I do not work on long-term projects; I focus on short-term projects (projects that are less than 3 months).</li>
  <li>I do not develop games, desktop applications, or mobile applications.</li>
  <li>I do not explore network vulnerabilities, as I am not a cybersecurity expert.</li>
  <li>I do not engage in large enterprise projects at this time; I only work on small to medium-sized projects.</li>
  <li>I do not accept rush deadlines; I prefer to work at a pace that ensures high-quality results.</li>
</ul>

<br/><br/>

<h4>Payment Terms</h4>
<ul>
  <li>I require a <b>downpayment</b> before starting any project. The amount will be discussed and agreed upon in advance (typically 50%).</li>
  <li>I only accept payments via <b>PayPal</b>, <b>Gcash</b>, or other platform-specific payment methods (as agreed upon).</li>
  <li>Failure to complete the full payment within the agreed time will result in project termination, regardless of the partial amount paid.</li>
</ul>

<br/><br/>

<h4>Completion Support</h4>
<span>I offer <b>7 days of free support</b> after project completion for minor issues. Any major issues will incur additional charges.</span>

<br/><br/>

<h4>Project Changes</h4>
<span>Any changes or additional requests during the development process will be subject to additional costs, as it may affect the project scope.</span>

<br/><br/>

<h4>Ownership</h4>
<span>Upon full payment, the client will own the final product. However, I must be credited as the creator of the website in the footer or a suitable location.</span>

<br/><br/>

<h4>Working Hours</h4>
<span>As a college student, I strive to balance my education with my freelance work. I typically work during evenings and weekends, but please note that project timelines may be affected by my academic schedule.</span>